top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Increase melee range in pvp combat.</span><hr size=1> Step into his path and wait.  Land backstab as you would on a jousting melee.  Usually works on circle runners. <p>Majestyk, <a href="http://Server3.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse">Rogue</a>, <a href="http://www.talonguard.org/shanks">Shanks</a>, <a href="http://vnboards.ign.com/board.asp?brd=5034">Vallon Zek!</a>We as Shanks, have chosen the hard path. In the hardness of it, is where we find the glory.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utularthemostill.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tular the Most Ill</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/1/01 8:50:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=221.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Increase melee range in pvp combat.</span><hr size=1> that doesn't really work thought Maj, either the caster will use his brain and avoid you or you just wont be able to kill him anyways because his pet is beating the crap out of you the whole time. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umadelinetz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Madeline TZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/2/01 12:57:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=221.topic&index=9>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://home.socal.rr.com/kayden/personalpiccolor.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT